query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, e.name as employeeName, e.specialization
FROM users u 
JOIN employees e ON u.id = e.userId 
WHERE u.email LIKE '%ghadahassen%' OR e.name LIKE '%غادة حسن%';
